node.text: it’s finally here! — we wanted to start off this new year being as raw and real as we possibly could. Clayton has been very open about his addiction & recovery in hopes to help others going through similar situations. I am so proud of him for teaching me to let go of our fears and the judgement of others and help end the stigma associated with opioid addiction. he is now 18 months sober, and continues to inspire me every day with his determination and passion to spread his message. this was definitely the hardest challenge we’ve ever had to face in our marriage, but we have come out stronger and closer than ever, and I have the Lord to thank for that. He truly can get you through ANYTHING. as you listen to our story, know that this is definitely the most vulnerable I’ve ever been on the internet, but if by sharing our story it even helps ONE person, it will all be worth it ♥️ video filmed & edited by our sweet friends, @cakewalkfilms #testimony #opioidaddiction #drugaddiction #addictionandrecovery #cakewalkfilms #thisisus

node.text: trying to make good decisions, even on vacay! we have woken up every morning & worked out to keep our body moving. fueling our body with good food (+ a few treats) & not forgetting our vitamins. exciting news - @ritual’s Essential for Women 18+ recently earned USP verification, which is a huge deal! (this helps ensure customers what’s on Ritual’s label is actually what’s in their capsules!) just another reason I love this company & their products. use code JESSCRUM10 for 10% off your first 3 months (valid for anything on their website)! #RitualPartner

we made it to cabo! ☀️ this is where you can find me the next couple of days, with a skinny jalapeño margarita in hand! these are a few of my favorite pool essentials:
+ a big hat
+ @tula’s newest mineral-based sunscreen☀️ (use code JESSCRUM for 15% off)
+ my kindle - just finished “Verity” and started “It Ends With Us” today! 
+ sunglasses
+ lip balm 
linking everything on the @shop.ltk app! #tulapartner

node.text: our new entryway is a vibe ✨ I just love how this space turned out. It’s warm, inviting and pulls in the modern touches we have throughout our house. these two pieces of art from @minted were the perfect touch to finish off the space. I love how they are sourced from a community of diverse artists from around the world & each purchase supports that individual artist! @minted gave us a code to get 20% off art frames through the end of the month (use code JESSFRAMES) // big thanks to @gather_in_grace for working her magic once again & creating a space we love! #mintedart #thecrummyhouse #entrywaydecor

node.text: 10 years together 🤍 we started dating when we were 19 years old, and it’s amazing to see the life we’ve been able to build together over the years. there’s no one else I’d rather going through life’s ups and downs with. in honor of our anniversary, we had a new wedding band designed with @diamondsdirect! today is the last day of their summer sale where you can save 20% off virtually everything! #DDpartner #diamondsdirect
